ZH: 山岭上的风景非常壮观。
EN: The scenery on the mountain ridge is very magnificent.

ZH: 我们在山岭上扎营过夜。
EN: We camped overnight on the mountain ridge.

ZH: 山岭的风很大，需要小心。
EN: The wind on the mountain ridge is strong, so be careful.

ZH: 鸟儿在山岭上飞翔，带来了生机。
EN: Birds flying on the mountain ridge bring vitality.

ZH: 山岭之巅是一处绝佳的观景点。
EN: The top of the mountain ridge is an excellent viewpoint.

ZH: 雪在山岭上反射阳光，发出耀眼的光芒。
EN: The snow on the mountain ridge reflects the sunlight, emitting a dazzling light.

ZH: 我们需要攀登那座险峻的山岭。
EN: We need to climb that steep mountain ridge.

ZH: 远处的山岭被云雾缭绕。
EN: The distant mountain ridge is shrouded in mist.

ZH: 山岭上的野花开得很美。
EN: Wildflowers on the mountain ridge bloom beautifully.

ZH: 雨后的山岭充满了清新的空气。
EN: The mountain ridge after the rain is filled with fresh air.

ZH: 山岭上有一条古老的小路。
EN: There is an ancient path on the mountain ridge.

ZH: 日出时分，山岭上洒满了金光。
EN: At sunrise, the mountain ridge is bathed in golden light.

ZH: 山岭对面是一片葱翠的森林。
EN: Over the mountain ridge is a lush forest.

ZH: 在山岭上，你可以俯瞰整个城市的风景。
EN: On the mountain ridge, you can overlook the scenery of the entire city.

ZH: 山岭上的草地上散发着清香。
EN: The grass on the mountain ridge releases a fresh scent.

ZH: 驱车经过山岭，感受到大自然的宁静。
EN: Driving through the mountain ridge, feeling the tranquility of nature.

ZH: 山岭被一片郁郁葱葱的树木所覆盖。
EN: The mountain ridge is covered with lush trees.

ZH: 在山岭上，你可以听到鸟儿的歌声。
EN: On the mountain ridge, you can hear the birds singing.

ZH: 山岭的地形崎岖不平，需要小心行走。
EN: The terrain of the mountain ridge is rugged, so be careful when walking.

ZH: 山岭上的遍野鲜花令人心情愉悦。
EN: The wildflowers all over the mountain ridge make people feel happy.
